Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Perfect access to Wayville Train Station

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The property is still one of the best fringe office buildings with an impressive foyer and internal atrium and fully refurbished amenities.  The available areas are stunning tenancies that have near new fitouts with a mix of workstations, meeting areas and fixed offices.
Located in the heart of the Fringe office market with easy access to the CBD.

Features: 

- On-site parks available. 
- High quality, corporate, modern office space.
- Parkland outlooks.
- Valuable access to the new Wayville train station.

Available Areas: 
Ground - 115 sqm (approx)
Ground - 181 sqm (approx)
First - 187.6 Sqm (approx)
First - 260.8 sqm (approx)

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: STILL ONE OF THE BEST ON THE FRINGE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Well appointed fringe office space that is centrally located at 81-83 Greenhill Road for lease. 

Consisting of 513.3sqm on the Ground Floor and is afforded with a functional fitout that provides an efficient layout plus having excellent natural light throughout. 

19 on-site undercover car parks are allocated to the tenancy.
